58
00:04:23,060 --> 00:04:25,920
(Crown Prince)

59
00:04:35,680 --> 00:04:41,360
Kill!

60
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,640
Your Highness, it's Wen Su.

61
00:05:23,640 --> 00:05:25,240
Why is he still alive?

62
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,600
You are the Crown Prince's aunt.

63
00:05:41,360 --> 00:05:42,200
He is merciful.

64
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,160
Knowing you love beauty,

65
00:05:43,800 --> 00:05:45,440
he ordered to leave your corpse intact.

66
00:05:50,200 --> 00:05:51,480
You should end yourself.

67
00:05:54,640 --> 00:05:56,280
Winner takes all.

68
00:05:57,600 --> 00:05:59,360
Just within a few days,

69
00:06:00,400 --> 00:06:02,120
we have exchanged our positions.

70
00:06:03,200 --> 00:06:05,040
I believe more in the manifestation of

71
00:06:05,520 --> 00:06:06,200
heavenly justice.

72
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,480
Heavenly justice?

73
00:06:20,320 --> 00:06:22,000
Since childhood, I have been well-read

74
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:23,400
with a profound knowledge.

75
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:25,880
Just because I am a woman,

76
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:28,280
I can only watch
incompetents gain power.

77
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:30,720
But a woman is only to marry,

78
00:06:31,040 --> 00:06:31,840
give birth,

79
00:06:31,840 --> 00:06:33,680
and become a tool.

80
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,800
Why?!

81
00:06:36,680 --> 00:06:38,360
So you harmed your elder brother

82
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:39,600
and intended a coup,

83
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,680
bringing Daqing to a crisis

84
00:06:42,680 --> 00:06:44,440
and ignoring blood and kinship?

85
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,400
What's wrong with that?

86
00:06:48,240 --> 00:06:49,400
The heaven is unjust,

87
00:06:49,960 --> 00:06:51,640
so I will take it myself.

88
00:06:52,320 --> 00:06:53,440
A decree can't be defied?

89
00:06:53,960 --> 00:06:55,520
I insist on fighting for it!

90
00:07:03,080 --> 00:07:03,880
Even as an emperor,

91
00:07:03,880 --> 00:07:05,040
you'll never be a wise ruler.

92
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:06,880
And no one will follow you.

93
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:11,360
You only have hatred.

94
00:07:13,320 --> 00:07:14,360
Right.

95
00:07:15,880 --> 00:07:17,560
How about you?

96
00:07:22,080 --> 00:07:24,560
You hate that I humiliated you

97
00:07:24,880 --> 00:07:27,640
and crushed your dignity.

98
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,120
Hate me then.

99
00:07:36,680 --> 00:07:38,600
Hatred lasts longer than love.

100
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:42,560
You are wrong.

101
00:07:46,320 --> 00:07:47,920
Even trapped in prison,

102
00:07:48,360 --> 00:07:50,440
I have never been defeated
by your humiliation.

103
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:54,560
I know what my heart desires.

104
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:57,840
And I know someone
in this world understands me

105
00:07:59,280 --> 00:08:00,920
and always stands by my side.

106
00:08:12,920 --> 00:08:14,640
I have loved passionately all my life.

107
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:17,040
For the late emperor,

108
00:08:18,000 --> 00:08:19,520
Daqing,

109
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,240
and the people,

110
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:24,840
I never felt a bit of guilt.

111
00:08:27,560 --> 00:08:29,400
I blame only time and fate

112
00:08:31,280 --> 00:08:33,600
for not fulfilling my heart's desires.

113
00:08:36,840 --> 00:08:39,200
In this lifetime,

114
00:08:40,400 --> 00:08:42,440
I don't need others to convict me.

115
00:09:26,676 --> 00:09:29,760
(By the Command of Heaven,
the Emperor decrees:)

116
00:09:29,760 --> 00:09:32,640
(In the 22nd year
of the rule of the Daqing Emperor,)

117
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:34,440
(Crown Prince accepted
the mandate of heaven,)

118
00:09:34,440 --> 00:09:37,800
(and followed the imperial edict
to ascend the throne.)

119
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,440
(Eldest Princess Zhao Qingcheng)

120
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:42,880
(attempted to overthrow the monarchy
and was sentenced according to the law.)

121
00:09:42,880 --> 00:09:45,080
(Reported and settled
after a long deliberation.)

122
00:09:45,080 --> 00:09:49,200
(Thus, I declare to the world
to let everyone know.)

123
00:09:53,939 --> 00:09:55,240
(Bianyang)

124
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,080
Congrats, Mr. Wen.

125
00:09:56,080 --> 00:09:56,480
Here.

126
00:09:56,480 --> 00:09:58,920
Mr. Wen Junior was appointed by His Majesty
as Assistant Minister of Revenue.

127
00:10:00,360 --> 00:10:01,800
And your name cleared.

128
00:10:01,800 --> 00:10:03,240
You regained Emperor's favor.

129
00:10:03,360 --> 00:10:04,400
As a close friend,

130
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:05,960
I share in the honor.

131
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,760
Thank you.

132
00:10:06,760 --> 00:10:07,960
Please come inside.

133
00:10:08,400 --> 00:10:09,000
Come inside.

134
00:10:09,000 --> 00:10:11,040
Father, Mother.

135
00:10:12,360 --> 00:10:12,760
Let's go.

136
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:14,240
Father,

137
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:16,200
