146
00:10:33,600 --> 00:10:34,880
- Baoyin...
- Baoyin...

147
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:35,400
She is...

148
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:36,360
Baoyin is...

149
00:10:44,840 --> 00:10:47,480
(Bianyang has been fully restored.)

150
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:50,360
(I come here every day
to tie a red ribbon,)

151
00:10:51,320 --> 00:10:53,040
(only hoping Mr. Wen Junior)

152
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:54,880
(to return home soon.)

153
00:10:54,880 --> 00:10:55,840
Baoyin.

154
00:10:56,160 --> 00:10:57,200
Baoyin.

155
00:10:59,600 --> 00:11:00,400
Baoyin.

156
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:02,520
Someone from the palace
wants to see you.

157
00:11:03,720 --> 00:11:04,640
Mr. Wen Junior...

158
00:11:04,840 --> 00:11:05,880
Must be news about him.

159
00:11:07,160 --> 00:11:07,800
Let's go.

160
00:11:26,640 --> 00:11:27,880
You're back.

161
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,560
You must be Lady Baoyin.

162
00:11:33,040 --> 00:11:34,280
Greetings, sir.

163
00:11:34,440 --> 00:11:35,640
I'm indeed Baoyin.

164
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,280
You have made contributions

165
00:11:42,280 --> 00:11:43,600
in finding the edict.

166
00:11:43,600 --> 00:11:45,280
These are rewards from His Majesty.

167
00:11:45,280 --> 00:11:46,680
Thanks for the rewards.

168
00:11:46,960 --> 00:11:48,160
I'm deeply grateful.

169
00:11:50,600 --> 00:11:51,720
I have one more thing

170
00:11:51,720 --> 00:11:53,640
to congratulate you.

171
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:57,280
I'm already overwhelmed.

172
00:11:57,800 --> 00:11:58,800
No wishful thinking.

173
00:11:58,800 --> 00:12:01,560
