about Mr. Wen's good news?

174
00:12:04,760 --> 00:12:06,440
Please, do not keep me
in suspense anymore.

175
00:12:06,880 --> 00:12:08,440
Mr. Wen guarded His Majesty well.

176
00:12:08,960 --> 00:12:09,760
